# Raven Language Recognition
*.rv linguist-language=Rust
*.rv linguist-detectable=true

# Documentation
docs/* linguist-documentation
README.md linguist-documentation
*.md linguist-documentation

# Generated files
target/* linguist-vendored
node_modules/* linguist-vendored
*.vsix linguist-generated

# Examples
examples/* linguist-detectable=true

# Golden baselines are diffed byte for byte across platforms: keep LF.
*.rv.out text eol=lf
*.rv text eol=lf
